Description: FancyZones-style window tiling for KDE Plasma
 PlasmaZones brings FancyZones-style window management to KDE Plasma 6.
 It allows users to create custom zone layouts and snap windows using
 drag-and-drop or keyboard shortcuts.
 .
 Features include:
  - Custom zone layout editor
  - KWin effect for visual feedback during window dragging
  - Keyboard navigation between zones
  - Per-monitor and per-activity layouts
  - System Settings integration (KCM)
